'''杰西昂·特雷尔·泰勒''' （{{Lang-en|Jayceon Terrell Taylor}}，{{bd|1979年|11月29日}}），因其艺名'''Game'''（最初为'''The Game'''）知名，是一名美国[[说唱歌手|说唱歌手]]。他因2005年的首张专辑《The Documentary》和两个[[格莱美奖|格莱美奖]]提名而一举成名。从那以后，他被认为是带领[[西海岸嘻哈|西海岸嘻哈]]融入主流，并和[[东海岸嘻哈|东海岸嘻哈]]向抗衡的驱动力。<ref>{{cite web |url=http://allhiphop.com/blogs/news/archive/2005/02/18/18129758.aspx |title=XXL Spotlights West Coast Hip-Hop In March Issue |accessdate=2007-07-20 |author=Clover Hope |date=2007-02-18 |work=Allhiphop |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20071106065519/http://allhiphop.com/blogs/news/archive/2005/02/18/18129758.aspx |archivedate=2007-11-06 }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url= http://www.dubcnn.com/features/editorials/2005wrapup/ |title= The West Coast Rap Up: 2005 |accessdate= 2007-01-27 |author= Conan Milne |year= 2005 |work= Dubcnn |archive-date= 2015-11-07 |archive-url= https://web.archive.org/web/20151107053104/http://www.dubcnn.com/features/editorials/2005wrapup/ |dead-url= no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.bet.com/Music/GAME%2BPlaytime%2BIs%2BOver.htm?wbc_purpose=Basic&WBCMODE=PresentationUnpublished |title=XXL Game: Playtime Is Over |accessdate=2007-10-08 |author=Kim Osorio |date=2006-03-21 |work=BET |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20060324060932/http://www.bet.com/Music/GAME%2BPlaytime%2BIs%2BOver.htm?wbc_purpose=Basic&WBCMODE=PresentationUnpublished |archivedate=2006-03-24 }}</ref>

除了发布了三张“[[公告牌二百强专辑榜|公告牌二百强专辑榜]]”排行榜冠军专辑外，Game还因和多名说唱歌手不和留下恶名。他的音乐大多属于[[黑幫嘻哈|黑幫嘻哈]]的主流，一种盛行于[[康普顿_(加利福尼亚州)|康普顿]]的嘻哈音乐形式。

